{"tid":854770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[共渡時艱] 中國飼料工業協會提議降低飼料蛋白質水平 並增設上限值","createTime":"2018-10-09T15:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T00:56:04.000Z","uid":119393,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7f8484f15a81148073872974125b88a66d7f6aa0","tid":854770,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.yicai.com/brief/100036751.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yicai.com%2Fbrief%2F100036751.html&d=M%2BbJOcERz1B5THZGK1yBrQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ce653b97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yicai.com/brief/100036751.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【中國飼料工業協會提議降低豬飼料中粗蛋白質水平，並增設上限值】中國飼料工業協會日前起草了《仔豬、生長育肥豬配合飼料》。其表示，我國是飼料資源短缺的國家，蛋白質飼料長期依賴進口，成為制約我國飼料工業和養殖業發展的瓶頸。隨著動物營養研究的深入，特別是低蛋白日糧配制技術的發展，在合理添加氨基酸和酶制劑的前提下，配合飼料中粗蛋白和磷的水平可以顯著降低。為推動飼料行業科技進步，減少飼料原料消耗，降低養殖業對環境造成的污染，對粗蛋白質、總磷在常規只設定下限值的基礎上增設了上限值。"},{"pid":"82ba1088f716eeb3e8d959a2539b86ae94af5ce5","tid":854770,"uid":63154,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"中國就簡單啦，三聚氰胺代替咪得"},{"pid":"897c337f41ac5818271c909721161df64a904bab","tid":854770,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"565c5147e103105b9c249b6166b42c3c2a679255","tid":854770,"uid":202383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"有毒飼料無害"},{"pid":"95f234a4d8a01454206ee574222cb830504e93ef","tid":854770,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"183029654f7561ac9a512e6c939373b60344cf38","tid":854770,"uid":38523,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"一句講晒<br />\n我地冇晒大豆咁咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad1bdbf01496f6fadb196e7f4771d7fa1b13141","tid":854770,"uid":62947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"人都要食草 啲豬仲想食乜？"},{"pid":"ad56df3c83dfafaabc9445c7ffb532bd0493dc50","tid":854770,"uid":35656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"冇左美國大豆呢個廉價高蛋白質來源，學人買巴西豆，雖然都係大豆，但問題營養價值人地美帝大豆基因改造後係高好多，結果捉撚左蟲入屎忽，搞到要降低飼料蛋白質水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c7cf923288926ce60512f3851de85ad67d7dcf","tid":854770,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"中國人根本無需要咁多營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b09dd3ff2e72ccdf9e087cacf438d73479bd1e0","tid":854770,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"小左蛋白質要養耐d結果咪仲晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812e52944b39908df2866de6e203635a4f6b8114","tid":854770,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"養出黎啲豬啲雞會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4178aa9737d10e71896f21614acfec07e6138571","tid":854770,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"cf02d3f5dd3b8fe417e08d3bb7b64e6f7b6ad158","tid":854770,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正啊  冇得食  食少d咪得囉"},{"pid":"30e45f6876c62a063baba2dfe1a92ca6d467c818","tid":854770,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"唔係食開屎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5569fad06c9f304cc0ebf33bcd620dde8d4750af","tid":854770,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse